latestIgtvVideos.title: 'SEXY' DOESN'T MEAN REVEALING
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I've heard alot of people say that to look sexy and attractive, you need to wear short clothes or reveal alot of skin and i really don't agree with that. Girls find it tricky to look sexy without wearing short clothes but im here to help you out !!
1. Sheer stockings - if you want to wear that cute dress but its too short, wear sheer stocking with it and you're sorted.
2. White tee and jeans - this basic outfit looks very hot when styled with gold jewellery and heels. 
3. Bright/bold lip- a bright/bold lip  according to me makes you look very attractive. I personally love them 💋
4. Mesh top - a mesh/sheer top is the best way to show skin without really exposing it. You can pair it with a Brallete ora tube top
5. All black outfits - there's nothing like an all black outfit. It makes you look sexy and slim at the same time 😋
6. Anything Satin- Satin is a very luxurious fabric and definitely my favourite!! A satin shirt or a slip dress looks very sexy and expensive 🤑

Last but not the least,confidence makes a woman stand out the most. No matter what you wear, own it girll 🤤
.
song - arms around you by xxx tentacion *I don't hold any rights for this music, only for creative purposes *
